public abstract class Actuator
extends Thread

Superclass for all specific actuators on a robot. Runs continously, waiting for commands. A driver of sorts

anand

run

public void run()
Start continuous execution of commands from the command queue Actuator will wait for a command to be present and execute it if suspended the actuator will continue running but ignore commands on exception the actuator will halt safely
